4
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:50,800
Boss.

5
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:52,819
This one?

6
00:03:53,139 --> 00:03:53,580
Alright.

7
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,919
Ten yuan.

8
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,780
