9
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,439
There you go.

10
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,639
Boss, take a look.

11
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:06,319
Revenue's down

12
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,480
