13
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,120
Summer break's here,

14
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,839
all the high school kids

15
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,839
come play

16
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,220
and run up tabs,

17
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,000
table fees,

18
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,800
sunflower seeds,

19
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,920
peanuts,

20
00:05:17,139 --> 00:05:18,000
everything.

21
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,519
I'm close to missing the electric bill.

22
00:05:21,339 --> 00:05:22,519
Can't we just scare 'em straight?

23
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,079
I... I'll get

24
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,600
Rocky to rough 'em up

25
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:26,279
next time?

26
00:05:30,939 --> 00:05:31,959
That girl

27
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:32,759
Yang mentioned,

28
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:34,639
she been around lately?

29
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:36,579
What girl?

30
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,060
Forget it.

31
00:05:40,379 --> 00:05:40,800
Got it.

32
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,339
Alright.

33
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:47,579
Lower your stance.

34
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:48,779
Yeah,

35
00:05:48,819 --> 00:05:49,759
relax your hand.

36
00:05:52,939 --> 00:05:53,379
Boss!

37
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:53,980
The girl.

38
00:05:54,339 --> 00:05:54,800
She's here.

39
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,860
That girl's here.

40
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:57,860
Look.

41
00:06:02,819 --> 00:06:03,239
Spread them?

42
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:03,639
Spread.

43
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,160
Good.

44
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,240
Yes.

45
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:06,180
Lower.

46
00:06:06,459 --> 00:06:06,819
Lower.

47
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:13,160
Relax your hand.

48
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:13,920
Yeah.

49
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:17,819
Nice shot.

50
00:06:25,339 --> 00:06:26,920
Can I book your boss as a coach?

51
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:29,740
Yi?

52
00:06:30,699 --> 00:06:32,839
He doesn't take coaching gigs.

53
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,139
Besides,

54
00:06:34,139 --> 00:06:35,060
dude's been through

55
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:36,019
some real stuff.

56
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,279
Casual play's

57
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,060
beneath him.

58
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:39,800
What kind of stuff?

59
00:06:40,060 --> 00:06:41,040
Well,

60
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,879
dunno the details.

61
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:43,000
But some guy

62
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,439
picked a fight here once,

63
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,000
Yi almost took him out

64
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,920
with a cue.

65
00:06:47,899 --> 00:06:48,620
Guy's definitely

66
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,920
got a past.

67
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,480
No way.

68
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,980
Yeah, pull your hand back.

69
00:06:56,899 --> 00:06:57,759
Nice shot.

70
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:58,980
Keep going.

71
00:07:01,939 --> 00:07:02,519
Hit this one.

72
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:03,839
This one first.

73
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,199
Alright.

74
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,360
I'll take over with her.

75
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:19,779
What's going on?

76
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,079
Come outside.

77
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:28,279
So this is

78
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,120
