81
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:38,899
Fine.

82
00:07:40,819 --> 00:07:41,519
I'll coach you

83
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,180
through this frame.

84
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:01,960
We can leave now.

85
00:09:04,059 --> 00:09:04,519
Sure.

86
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:19,139
This isn't a place for you.

87
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,580
Stay away from those guys.

88
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,320
Why should I listen to you?

89
00:09:30,259 --> 00:09:30,779
Are you deliberately

90
00:09:30,779 --> 00:09:31,500
trying to get on my nerves?

91
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,440
Me? You're the one

92
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,340
who's always had it out for me.

93
00:09:39,019 --> 00:09:39,600
Yeah.

94
00:09:40,179 --> 00:09:41,139
As long as you're here,

95
00:09:41,419 --> 00:09:42,159
I can't relax.

96
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,000
You get under my skin.

97
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,620
Clear enough,

98
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:45,240
Miao Jing?

99
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,480
Can't relax?

100
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,200
Why do you even care?

101
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:54,399
Right.

102
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,320
None of my business.

103
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:00,440
Hour's up.

104
00:10:00,779 --> 00:10:01,759
Closing time, Boss Chen.

105
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:03,100
You heading home?

106
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,860
Can I catch a ride?

107
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:10,320
No.

108
00:10:11,899 --> 00:10:12,679
Not going home tonight.

109
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:53,639
Yi,

110
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,220
sleeping here again?

111
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:58,919
Come on, have breakfast.

112
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,980
I picked these out for you.

113
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:02,519
Hurry.

114
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,139
Soy milk,

115
00:11:05,139 --> 00:11:05,559
buns,

116
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,580
they'll get cold. Hurry up.

117
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,360
Here.

118
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,580
Who's in charge?

119
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,139
Routine inspection.

120
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,500
Business license,

121
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:30,879
fire permit, you got them?

122
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:32,740
Yes,

123
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:33,840
officer. Right this way.

124
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,120
I'll show you.

125
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,840
Fire safety was inspected last week?

126
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,639
That's correct.

127
00:11:54,059 --> 00:11:55,220
Surveillance all working?

128
00:11:55,419 --> 00:11:55,919
Yep.

129
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:57,759
Full coverage inside,

130
00:11:57,759 --> 00:11:58,559
infrared cameras

131
00:11:58,559 --> 00:11:59,519
outside too.

132
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:08,600
A fruit knife

133
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:09,960
isn't a controlled weapon, right?

134
00:12:11,379 --> 00:12:11,980
No, it isn't.

135
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:13,879
But we've had reports

136
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:15,799
of gang activity here.

137
00:12:16,299 --> 00:12:17,159
Any truth to that?

138
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,879
Just a customer disagreement,

139
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,039
a small argument.

140
00:12:23,379 --> 00:12:24,139
Hardly gang activity.

141
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:26,159
Didn't think

142
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:27,240
this would bother the police.

143
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:32,419
You run a legitimate business.

144
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:33,740
Stay away from

145
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:34,960
anything illegal.

146
00:12:38,419 --> 00:12:39,320
Thanks for the heads-up, officer.

147
00:12:39,519 --> 00:12:40,080
We will.

148
00:12:41,279 --> 00:12:41,740
Captain Zhou,

149
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:43,480
