150
00:12:45,279 --> 00:12:45,740
Let's go.

151
00:12:46,980 --> 00:12:47,600
Take care.

152
00:12:55,059 --> 00:12:56,519
Why'd he show up himself?

153
00:12:58,279 --> 00:12:59,059
Tell everyone

154
00:12:59,059 --> 00:12:59,820
we're closed today.

155
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:05,759
Yi,

156
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:07,279
come over for dinner tonight.

157
00:13:07,519 --> 00:13:08,600
I'll make salt and pepper ribs.

158
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,080
When Li Qiao and I move,

159
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:13,159
