160
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,899
She'll cook you something proper.

161
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,600
Hey, Bo,

162
00:13:20,220 --> 00:13:21,320
send me that real estate

163
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:21,960
agent's contact.

164
00:13:25,419 --> 00:13:26,340
What for?

165
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:30,960
I wanna rent out

166
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,639
my apartment.

167
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:32,679
Rent it out?

168
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:34,080
Did Miao Jing drive you crazy?

169
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,080
Hello, sir.

170
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,000
Here about a property?

171
00:13:52,419 --> 00:13:53,600
Yeah, I'm meeting Manager Xu.

172
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,779
I have an apartment to rent out.

173
00:13:54,879 --> 00:13:55,620
Mr. Chen,

174
00:13:56,259 --> 00:13:57,080
I'm Manager Xu.

175
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:58,240
Please, have a seat.

176
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,120
Liu, water please.

177
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:00,779
Mr. Chen,

178
00:14:00,779 --> 00:14:01,440
sit.

179
00:14:02,179 --> 00:14:02,759
Here's the contract.

180
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,279
We went over

181
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:05,879
the details

182
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:06,820
