183
00:14:07,419 --> 00:14:08,139
It's an

184
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,279
older neighborhood,

185
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:09,820
and

186
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,720
amenities

187
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,620
are dated.

188
00:14:11,779 --> 00:14:12,820
Rent might not

189
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,240
