190
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:15,779
That's fine.

191
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,039
Lower rent is okay.

192
00:14:17,179 --> 00:14:18,000
I just need it fast.

193
00:14:18,379 --> 00:14:19,059
Fast?

194
00:14:20,039 --> 00:14:20,600
Honestly,

195
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:22,220
you'd make

196
00:14:22,419 --> 00:14:23,379
