198
00:14:25,019 --> 00:14:25,960
If you listed it for sale...

199
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,039
Rental only. Not for sale.

200
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,120
Not for sale?

201
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,600
Short or long term, doesn't matter.

202
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:33,200
I can cut

203
00:14:33,279 --> 00:14:34,059
rent and utilities.

204
00:14:34,799 --> 00:14:35,539
Just make it fast.

205
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:38,440
You're making a lot of concessions.

206
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,039
Do you have tenant requirements?

207
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:43,480
I just need you to do me one favor.

208
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,240
Who is it?

209
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,200
Hello!

210
00:15:03,559 --> 00:15:04,179
Hi,

211
00:15:04,659 --> 00:15:05,120
well,

212
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,120
I'm Manager Xu

213
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,080
from

214
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:07,559
Yi'anjia Real Estate.

215
00:15:08,419 --> 00:15:09,419
Not buying, thanks.

216
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:11,019
No, don't get me wrong.

217
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:13,019
Mr. Chen asked me to view the apartment.

218
00:15:13,539 --> 00:15:14,600
Mr. Chen?

219
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,259
Didn't he text you?

220
00:15:33,919 --> 00:15:35,360
Chen Yi sent you, right?

221
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,039
That's right.

222
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:36,840
Come on in.

223
00:15:36,899 --> 00:15:37,519
Sure, thanks.

224
00:15:37,519 --> 00:15:38,519
Take a look around.

225
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:39,399
Okay.

226
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:41,960
Nice big living room.

227
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:43,139
Yeah.

228
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,120
Sorry about

229
00:15:45,399 --> 00:15:47,240
