230
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,200
I just fixed it.

231
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:48,919
No problem.

232
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:49,600
Works fine.

233
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,799
The balcony has

234
00:15:51,799 --> 00:15:53,039
great natural light,

235
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,320
feels nice

236
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,840
in the morning.

237
00:15:57,679 --> 00:15:59,399
Master bedroom's spacious too,

238
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,000
all furniture stays.

239
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,379
Bed, wardrobe,

240
00:16:02,379 --> 00:16:03,399
everything.

241
00:16:03,919 --> 00:16:04,519
Got it.

242
00:16:04,919 --> 00:16:05,899
Check the hallway,

243
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:08,000
nice high ceilings, right?

244
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:09,279
Yeah, not bad.

245
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,480
This is second bedroom.

246
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,519
Second bedroom's smaller,

247
00:16:12,519 --> 00:16:13,639
but the window's great,

248
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,600
really airy,

249
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,159
really nice.

250
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,179
Now

251
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:19,600
the kitchen.

252
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:21,340
Look,

253
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,679
it's separate,

254
00:16:22,679 --> 00:16:24,240
so fumes

255
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,440
don't spread.

256
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,080
Perfect for

257
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,159
family meals.

258
00:16:28,519 --> 00:16:29,440
Over here,

259
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,360
messy as it is,

260
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:34,120
lots of storage.

261
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:37,200
This'll sell for a good price,

262
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:37,960
right?

263
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:38,919
Come,

264
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:40,360
let's see the rest.

265
00:17:18,019 --> 00:17:18,539
I already

266
00:17:18,539 --> 00:17:19,839
talked to the agent.

267
00:17:20,380 --> 00:17:21,500
I'm selling this place in a few days.

268
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:23,940
Haicheng has everything you need.

269
00:17:24,819 --> 00:17:25,920
Go back, live your life.

270
00:17:27,259 --> 00:17:27,880
We're done

271
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:29,299
with each other.

272
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,700
What about you?

273
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:34,700
None of your business.

274
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,359
I didn't say you have to leave now.

275
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:53,160
I'll rent you

276
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:55,559
