279
00:18:00,019 --> 00:18:01,359
Lots of dust.

280
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:02,480
Here, wipe your face.

281
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,279
Right.

282
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:06,940
Mr. Chen, you're here too.

283
00:18:07,319 --> 00:18:07,799
This place

284
00:18:07,799 --> 00:18:09,119
hasn't been dusted.

285
00:18:09,359 --> 00:18:10,779
Got dust in my eye earlier.

286
00:18:11,859 --> 00:18:13,460
Since you've thought this through,

287
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,059
it's your name on the deed,

288
00:18:15,279 --> 00:18:16,960
I'll get you a good price.

289
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:20,039
Consider it payback for letting me stay.

290
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,480
Miss Miao!

291
00:18:24,180 --> 00:18:24,759
Coming!

292
00:18:24,759 --> 00:18:25,519
Here, take these.

293
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:27,279
Come in, hurry.

294
00:18:27,279 --> 00:18:27,880
Alright.

295
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,059
Hello. We spoke on the phone.

296
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:30,799
Take a look.

297
00:18:30,799 --> 00:18:31,579
Take a look

298
00:18:31,579 --> 00:18:32,400
at the living room.

299
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:33,480
That's the balcony,

300
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,700
great light,

301
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:35,500
lots of space.

302
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,079
Wanna check it out?

303
00:18:36,079 --> 00:18:36,599
Sure.

304
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:36,980
Okay.

305
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:38,039
Come have a look.

306
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,940
-Nice.
-It's huge.

